</ul>
<hr>
<a name="NextMeeting">
<h2>When is the next meeting?</h2>

The Next meeting date is 
unknown, probably in late Februaru or early March.


<hr>
<a name="Agenda">
<h3>Agenda next meeting</h3>
*** The Agenda is <i>always</i> Under construction***
<br>
Potential topics of interest include:
<ul>
</ul>
<p>
There is no standardized time frame for meetings, but most meetings
run from 3 to about 5:30, and we usually then find a resturant for
food, drinks, and further discussion. Some of the resturant conversations
have been wonderful and lasted for hours.


<h3>Don't forget</h3>
<ul>
