 Report of the Business-Government Forum on Global Cryptogoraphy Policy </a>
Note: the attendee list contains many names that are familiar, including
government and commercial folks.
<li><A HREF="http://www.bsa.org/bsa"> US Commerce Deptartment survey of crypto policy </A>
