<DOCHDR>
http://isse.gmu.edu:80/students/pfarrell/nist/post.bu960117.html 129.174.40.15 19970123195610 text/html 3456
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Thu, 23 Jan 1997 19:54:59 GMT
