<A HREF="http://www.isse.gmu.edu/students/pfarrell/disclaimer.html"> 
PDF</a> September 1, 1995.  Backto <a href="../hotlist.html">Pat's hotlist</a> Backto <a href="../index.html">Pat's homepage</a>
