<td ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=MIDDLE>April<BR>1994</td><td ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=MIDDLE>Pharmacyclics</t><td>MRI contrast medium</td><td> n.a.</td><td>n.a.</td><tr>
                                       
