<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Mitsubishi Chemical Corporation</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF><H1>Mitsubishi Chemical Corporation</H1>
<H3>Corporate Profile</H3>
