  <IMG BORDER=3 WIDTH=425 HEIGHT=250 SRC="http://www.vicinity.com/gif?&CT=38.39319:-120.79495:20000&IC=38.39319:-120.79495:Smallcross:Crooks+'n'+Nooks&FAM=mapblast"></A>
