<P><FONT SIZE=+1><B>W</B></FONT>elcome to the membership directory of the Northern California Independent Booksellers Association. Here you will find an alphabetical listing of dozens of member bookstores scattered throughout the East Bay and neighboring communities. Stores are designated as being NEW, USED or NEW & USED as well as GENERAL interest or SPECIALTY shops. Additional store specialties are also noted. If you know the name of the bookstore you are looking for, simply click on the appropriate letter of the alphabet to move around this page. These alphabetical links will take you to the beginning of that letter's listing.

